05_Cognitive

Subjective Graph Literacy

SGL scores ranged from 10 to 58 with an average score of 33 (red dotted line).

There was a signfiicant decline in graph literacy with age, r = -0.224, p = 0.001

Numeracy

Numeracy scores ranged from 0 to 14 with an average score of 9 (red dotted line).

There was a significant increase in numeracy with age, r = 0.172, p = 0.013.
